name: TUI BLUE Tuy Hoa - Wellness & Retreat Hotel
location: 02 Hai Duong Street, Binh Ngoc, Tuy Hoà, Việt Nam
description:
Standing tall on Hai Duong street, TUI BLUE Tuy Hoa - Wellness & Retreat Hotel offers contemporary accommodation in Tuy Hoa. Boasting a swimming pool, the hotel offers a vast variety of restaurants and a fitness centre. Guests can enjoy free parking on site.

Featuring free WiFi access, all well-appointed units are decorated in white shade with hints of light brown from the fabric and black from the furnishings. All units enjoy air conditioning, a cable flat-screen TV and minibar. En suite bathroom is equipped with a bathtub, hairdryer, slippers and free toieltries.

For relaxation, guests can head to the services: JJIMJILBANG, ONSEN, TAICHI GARDEN, SPA & BEAUTY. Staff at 24-hour front desk can assist you with luggage storage and express check-in/check-out. Tour arrangement, car/motorbike rental and airport transfer can be made at the tour desk.

Available for all-day dining, The Restaurant serves a delectable spread of international and Asian delights. Meals are well complemented with a selection of global wines from Australia, France and Italy. Room service can be requested.

Tuy Hoa Catholic Church and Bao Tinh Church are within 5-minute drive from TUI BLUE Tuy Hoa - Wellness & Retreat Hotel, while Tuy Hoa public beach can be reached within a 10-minute drive. A 15-minute drive can take you to the nearest airport, Tuy Hoa Airport.

name: Nui Thom Ecolodge
location: Nui Thom, An Phu, Tuy Hoà, Việt Nam
description:
Spread across 50 hectares of picturesque landscapes, Nui Thom Ecolodge features an 800 square-metre outdoor pool with a waterfall and hot tub. The resort has a spa, tennis courts and a fitness centre. Guests can access the private beach which is 2 km away by resort buggy, Free buggy for all guest from Resort to the beach.

The air-conditioned rooms offer a blend of classic wood furnishings and Vietnamese design. Fitted with a tea/coffee maker, they feature a charming bath area with a skylight and bathtub.

Nestled on Thom Hill, Nui Thom Ecolodge is a 10-minute drive from Tuy Hoa City 0 Phy Yen Province and a 20-minute drive from Tuy Hoa Airport. It is 90 km from Qui Nhơn City and has free parking.

The day spa provides pampering massages, facials, as well as a sauna. Guests may enjoy the use of private karaoke rooms and free Wi-Fi in public areas.

Daily breakfast, fresh seafood dishes and Western/Asian menus are on offer at the 2 restaurants. The resort also has a pool bar, lobby bar and 24-hour room service

name: Apec Mandala Phú Yên
location: Apec Mandala Phú Yên, Đại lộ Hùng Vương, Phường 7, TP Tuy Hòa, Phú Yên, Tuy Hoà, Việt Nam
description:
Tọa lạc ở Tuy Hoà, cách Bãi biển Tuy Hòa 19 phút đi bộ, Apec Mandala Phú Yên cung cấp chỗ nghỉ có khu vườn, chỗ đậu xe riêng, sân hiên và nhà hàng. Ngoài quầy bar, khách sạn 5 sao này còn có các phòng với điều hòa được trang bị Wi-Fi miễn phí, trong đó mỗi phòng đều có phòng tắm riêng. Chỗ nghỉ này cung cấp dịch vụ phòng và quầy lễ tân 24 giờ cho khách.

Tại khách sạn, tất cả các phòng đều có bàn làm việc. Mỗi phòng đều có TV màn hình phẳng, ngoài ra một số căn tại Apec Mandala Phú Yên có view thành phố. Tại chỗ nghỉ, phòng nào cũng có ga trải giường và khăn tắm.

Sân bay Tuy Hòa cách 6 km.
